1
00:00:01,986 --> 00:00:03,723
给可怜的瘸子赏点东西吧?
Anything for a poor cripple?

2
00:00:03,741 --> 00:00:06,557
我奉拿撒勒人耶稣的名
In the name of Jesus of Nazareth,

3
00:00:06,583 --> 00:00:08,651
叫你起来行走
rise up and walk.

4
00:00:10,087 --> 00:00:13,022
神立耶稣为主 为弥赛亚了
God made Jesus Lord and Messiah.

5
00:00:13,056 --> 00:00:14,223
让他们闭嘴
Silence them now.

6
00:00:14,258 --> 00:00:16,125
啊! 彼得!
Aah! Peter!

7
00:00:16,159 --> 00:00:19,395
约翰... 我们可能永远出不去了
John... We may never leave here.

8
00:00:19,429 --> 00:00:22,164
彼拉多明天打算亲自造访神庙
Pilate will visit the temple on Pentecost.

9
00:00:22,199 --> 00:00:25,267
波阿斯 这就是先知们所说的可憎之事
Boaz, this is the abomination the prophets talked about.

10
00:00:25,302 --> 00:00:26,636
那我们下手的时间就到了
Then our time has come.

11
00:00:28,405 --> 00:00:29,605
哥尼流!
Cornelius!

12
00:00:29,640 --> 00:00:31,080
但愿你死得其所
I hope your cause is worth dying for.

13
00:00:31,108 --> 00:00:33,042
愿你如此
I hope yours is.

14
00:00:33,076 --> 00:00:35,277
有人发现马尔库斯·德鲁苏斯被杀害了
Marcus Drusus was found murdered.

15
00:00:35,312 --> 00:00:36,846
我们在附近逮捕了一伙人
We've arrested a group of men in the area.

16
00:00:36,880 --> 00:00:38,481
处决他们
Execute them.

17
00:00:38,515 --> 00:00:40,750
把杀手交出来
Deliver the assassin to us.

18
00:00:40,784 --> 00:00:43,652
他荣光之国的名字 是应当称颂的
Blessed be the name of his glorious kingdom

19
00:00:43,687 --> 00:00:45,688
直到永永远远
forever and ever.

